---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for the VDA 231-301 website.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">

    <div class="mb-8 text-sm text-[#5a7a65]">
      🇩🇪 <a href={`${base}datenschutz/`} class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">Deutsche Version: Datenschutzerklärung</a>
    </div>

    <h1
      class="mb-8 text-balance"
      style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 2.25rem; color: #0d3d20; line-height: 1.15;"
    >
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20] mb-3">1. Data Controller</h2>
      <address class="not-italic text-[#2a3a30] leading-relaxed text-base">
        VDA 231-301 Project Group<br />
        c/o Verband der Automobilindustrie e.V.<br />
        Behrenstraße 35<br />
        10117 Berlin<br />
        Germany<br /><br />
        E-mail: <a href="mailto:info@vda.de" class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">info@vda.de</a>
      </address>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20] mb-3">2. Hosting</h2>
      <p class="text-[#2a3a30] leading-relaxed text-base mb-3">
        This website is hosted via <strong>GitHub Pages</strong> (GitHub Inc., 88 Colin P Kelly Jr St,
        San Francisco, CA 94107, USA). When you visit this website, GitHub may automatically collect and
        store server log data, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#2a3a30] text-base space-y-1 mb-3">
        <li>IP address of the requesting device</li>
        <li>Date and time of the request</li>
        <li>URL of the requested page</li>
        <li>HTTP status code and transferred data volume</li>
        <li>Browser type and operating system (user agent)</li>
        <li>Referring URL</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-[#2a3a30] leading-relaxed text-base">
        This data is processed by GitHub as the hosting provider. For details, please refer to
        <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">GitHub's Privacy Statement</a>.
        The legal basis for this processing is Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interests in operating a
        technically functional website).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20] mb-3">3. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p class="text-[#2a3a30] leading-relaxed text-base">
        This website does not use cookies. We do not employ any analytics tools, tracking scripts, or
        third-party services that collect personal data on our behalf.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20] mb-3">4. Your Rights under GDPR</h2>
      <p class="text-[#2a3a30] leading-relaxed text-base mb-3">
        Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) you have the following rights regarding
        any personal data processed in connection with this website:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[#2a3a30] text-base space-y-1">
        <li><strong>Right of access</strong> (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to rectification</strong> (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to erasure</strong> ("right to be forgotten", Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to restriction of processing</strong> (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to data portability</strong> (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to object</strong> (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20] mb-3">5. Right to Lodge a Complaint</h2>
      <p class="text-[#2a3a30] leading-relaxed text-base">
        You have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority. The competent authority
        for the VDA is the Berlin Commissioner for Data Protection and Freedom of Information
        (<a href="https://www.datenschutz-berlin.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">www.datenschutz-berlin.de</a>).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20] mb-3">6. Contact for Data Protection Enquiries</h2>
      <p class="text-[#2a3a30] leading-relaxed text-base">
        For any questions regarding data protection, please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:info@vda.de" class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">info@vda.de</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
